        <updateDate>2022-03-11T16:17:47Z</updateDate>
        <text><![CDATA[ <p><b>Community Driven Recovery for Puerto Rico Act</b></p> <p>This bill establishes an Office for Equitable, Transparent, and Accountable Puerto Rico Reconstruction which shall be headed by a Puerto Rico Civil Society Task Force. </p> <p>The task force shall be an independent federal entity established to ensure accountability of and local oversight over reconstruction efforts in Puerto Rico.</p> <p>The office shall be funded by the administrative portion of the estimated Community Development Block Grant Disaster Recovery disbursements for Puerto Rico.</p>]]></text>
      </summary>
